data.description: DELAND: BRANDYWINE ; UPGRADES ; MOVE IN READY ; SPACIOUS LOT ; 2 SCREENED PORCHES: What a great opportunity to own this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom homes with over 1,600 sq ft on a spacious .35 acre lot. The pathway leads to the screened front porch which is a great place to enjoy morning coffee and has been newly painted and a new fan has been added to keep you cool. The entry way features built in shelving that is perfect for displaying your pictures and decorations! The Living room is spacious and features re-engineered wood floors which are AMAZING! Sliding doors lead to the screened back porch and give great views of the private backyard. The upgraded eat in kitchen boasts new painted cabinets, new tile back splash, new stainless steel refrigerator, new sink & hardware and re-piping. The breakfast area is perfect for early morning breakfast. The dining area has plenty of space for your table and china cabinet and has easy flow to the kitchen and living room. The Master bedroom has also been newly painted and features easy to maintain laminate floors. The Master bathroom has been updated with a new toilet and new tile work in the shower. Additional bedrooms are spacious and the guest bathroom also has a new toilet and paint. The laundry room is HUGE! There is so much extra space for storage or to make into a craft room! The back porch is the perfect spot to relax after a long day. The backyard is private and there is plenty of room for the pets to run or to add a playground. The Storage shed is perfect for outdoor tools. Don't wait! Make your private appointment today to see all this property has to offer YOU!
